# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy to `.env` and fill in. `.env` is gitignored.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Contact form — Web3Forms access key.
# 1. Go to https://web3forms.com/#start
# 2. Enter max.richter.dev@proton.me → receive a free access key
# 3. Paste here. Every form submission is forwarded to that inbox.
#
# The PUBLIC_ prefix exposes the key to the client bundle — that's required
# because the form posts directly from the browser. Web3Forms access keys
# are designed to be public and are scoped per-destination; they cannot be
# abused to send to another address.
PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
